  "description": "The Nexus revelation. Duo mode with both voices on VA — the interval between two held notes becomes a synthesis parameter. HAMMER at -0.5 drives cross-FM where the modulation ratio IS the musical interval. Play a perfect fifth: the FM ratio locks to 3:2. Play a tritone: dissonance erupts. Every chord voicing sounds structurally different. The instrument reads your harmony.",
